
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
    <iframe width="560" height="300" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" src=<%="http://www.viki.com/player/" + videoId%>>
    </iframe>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6 text-center">
    <div class="panel panel-info">
      <div class="panel-heading">
        <h3 class="panel-title">Original Subs</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-body">
        <h4>1</h4>
        <p>00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:03,553</p>
        <p>What were you saying?</p>
        <h4>2</h4>
        <p>00:05:14,400 --> 00:05:16,550</p>
        <p>That the reason why dirt spoon Cinderella was able to meet a gold spoon man was because she went to the ball</p>
        <h4>3</h4>
        <p>00:05:16,840 --> 00:05:19,115</p>
        <p>Well, that audacity!</p>
        <h4>4</h4>
        <p>00:05:19,400 --> 00:05:21,834</p>
        <p>Indeed. Makes me feel like the colour of my red shirt.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-md-6 text-center">
    <div class="panel panel-info">
      <div class="panel-heading">
        <h3 class="panel-title">CrowdSub</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-body">
        <%# Creating new comments form%>
        <form class="" action=<%="/videos/" +videoId%> method="post">
          <div class="form-group">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-12 text-left">
                <label for="timing">Timing</label>
              </div>
            </div>
            <input type="number" class="form-control" id="timing" name="timing" placeholder="Enter Timing number">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-12 text-left">
                <small id="timingHelp" class="form-text text-muted">
                  This is the no. above the time range
                </small>
              </div>
            </div>
            <br>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-12 text-left">
                <label for="sugsub">Suggested Subs</label>
              </div>
            </div>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="sugsub" name="sugsub" placeholder="e.g. That's the reason why poor Cinderella was able to meet a rich man...">
            <br>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-12 text-left">
                <label for="reason">Reason</label>
              </div>
            </div>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="reason" name="reason" placeholder="e.g. Quality of spoons are a literal translation of wealth">
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">CrowdSub!</button>
        </form>
        <%# For the upvoting after comment is made%>
        <div id="topic" class="upvote">
          <a class="upvote"></a>
          <span class="count">0</span>
          <a class="downvote"></a>
          <a class="star"></a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
